data.value:
The National Security Agney (NSA) holds a CodeBreaker Challenge each year. Participants from across the world get to reverse engineering and "break" software during tasks in the challenge.
This year (2016), there were 6 tasks. This program was coded to solve tasks of the challenge. You can modify parameters according to variables used in your binaries. Hope you find this useful. Do read the about section.
